data.description: Beautifully maintained 2-Bedroom, 2.5-Bathroom End Unit Townhouse with Finished Basement.  Notice the curb appeal as you arrive to find landscaped garden beds that wrap around the side of the home.  Two designated parking spots can be found right out front of this PREMIUM, CUL-DE-SAC LOT.  Enter into the living room where you will find chair rail, crown molding, and HARDWOOD FLOORS that run throughout the entire first floor.  Located right off the living room is the kitchen and dining area.  The kitchen features: GRANITE countertops, STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES, tile backsplash, an island, a pantry & a ceiling fan.  Sliders from the kitchen lead to the deck, which steps down to the yard.  This premium lot backs to woods and is completely private on one side.  Back inside and also on the first floor is a powder room.  Head upstairs to find 2 spacious bedrooms and 2 full baths.  The master bedroom boasts a WALK-IN CLOSET and a full master bath.  The 2nd bedroom offers jack-and-jill access to the full hall bath, which features tile floors and a linen closet.  Looking for more space? Find it here in the FINISHED BASEMENT!  The basement offers a large, open area that can be used as a family room, playroom, home office, etc.  An unfinished section provides plenty of storage space and houses the laundry facilities.  Not only has this home been very well maintained, it also has several great recent updates!  Notable features include: BRAND NEW HVAC, BRAND NEW WATER HEATER, all newer carpet throughout (2-3 years old), 2 small storage sheds included, & ALL APPLIANCES INCLUDED!  CONVENIENTLY LOCATED near tons of stores and restaurants, and just minutes from major roadways for ease of commute.  Don’t wait, be sure to book your tour today before it’s too late.
